Ideal for an apartment or small space, this Julia convertible futon from DHP provides extra seating or sleeping space for overnight guests. When used as a sofa, this faux-leather futon has a convenient cup holder for storing your favorite beverage, and a multi-position back allows you to find the most comfortable position for watching movies.
